title: 2020 CFB Pick Em Week 15
description:
El Pres, Big Cat and Rico Bosco are back for another week of picks. Despite rumors and losing 13 units on Marshall, Rico was in studio to face the critics. We discuss the potential CFP scenarios, specifically whether Ohio State deserves to be in despite the Michigan cancellation!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
